<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.8.5">
<l>kaṇkaḷāl kāṇa varuṅkoleṉ ṟācaiyāṉ</l>
<l>maṇkoṇṭa vāmaṉa ṉēṟa makiḻntucel</l>
<l>paṇkoṇṭa puḷḷiṉ ciṟakoli pāvittu</l>
<l>tiṇkoḷḷa vōrkkuṅ kiṭanteṉ cevikaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>My ears repose [and] listen steadfastely,</l>
<l>experiencing the sound of the wings of the serviceable bird</l>
<l>that goes joyfully while the dwarf who took the earth mounts [it],</l>
<l>with the longing “will he come [for me] to see with [my own] eyes?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
